title: The Scribbler. Official Movie Trailer #1 [HD] (2014)
description:
In theaters: September 19th, 2014

Description:

The Scribbler follows Suki (Katie Cassidy), a young woman confronting her destructive mental illness using "The Siamese Burn," an experimental machine designed to eliminate multiple personalities. The closer Suki comes to being "cured," she's haunted by a thought... what if the last unwanted identity turns out to be her?

Director: John Suits

Writers: Dan Schaffer

Actors: Katie Cassidy, Michelle Trachtenberg, Eliza Dushku, Gina Gershon, Sasha Grey, Garrett Dillahunt, Michael Imperioli, Billy Campbell

Genre: Science Fiction, Action and Adventure, Thriller

Run Time: 1 hour 30 minutes
